'''咽喉反流'''（Laryngopharyngeal reflux，縮寫 LPR）<ref name=cornell>[http://www.nycornell.org/ent/Laryngopharyngeal.reflux.html Laryngopharyngeal Reflux] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nycornell.org/ent/Laryngopharyngeal.reflux.html |date=20160417134059 }}, New York-Presbyterian Hospital, Weill Cornell Medical Center</ref><ref name=about>[http://heartburn.about.com/od/gastrictractdisorders/a/whatis_LPR.htm Laryngopharyngeal Reflux (LPR)] {{Wayback|url=http://heartburn.about.com/od/gastrictractdisorders/a/whatis_LPR.htm |date=20160303194317 }}, About.com</ref>，又稱為喉咽回流、咽喉逆流症、咽喉胃酸逆流、胃食管外反流疾病（extraesophageal reflux disease，縮寫 EERD）<ref>{{cite journal |author=Kahrilas PJ |title=Maximizing outcome of extraesophageal reflux disease |journal=Am J Manag Care |volume=6 |issue=16 Suppl |pages=S876–82 |date=October 2000 |pmid=11184658 |doi= |url=}}</ref>，是指[[胃酸|胃酸]]逆行流到上呼吸[[胃腸道|消化道]]的現象，如此現象會導致多種症狀，如[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]、[[發音困難|聲音嘶啞]]和[[喘鳴|喘息]]，等等症狀。咽喉反流為[[哮喘|哮喘]]的相關的[[合併症|合併症]]。<ref name=Cazzola-3013>{{cite journal |vauthors=Cazzola M, Segreti A, Calzetta L, Rogliani P |title=Comorbidities of asthma: current knowledge and future research needs |journal=Current Opinion in Pulmonary Medicine |volume=19 |issue=1 |pages=36–41 |year=2013 |pmid=23114561 |doi=10.1097/MCP.0b013e32835b113a |url=http://www.researchgate.net/profile/Mario_Cazzola/publication/232745343_Comorbidities_of_asthma_current_knowledge_and_future_research_needs/links/0912f50ddc0a8dd1f9000000.pdf |access-date=2016-08-21 |archive-date=2016-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823002337/https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Mario_Cazzola/publication/232745343_Comorbidities_of_asthma_current_knowledge_and_future_research_needs/links/0912f50ddc0a8dd1f9000000.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

雖然[[胃灼熱|胃灼熱]]是人們[[胃食管反流病|胃食管反流病]]（GERD）的主要症狀，然而胃灼熱存在的患者之 LPR 少於50％。用來描述這種情況的其他術語包括「非典型回流」、<ref>{{Cite web | title = MARCI-Kids Midwest Acid Reflux Children's Institute | url = http://www.marci-kids.com/eerintro.html | publisher =  | date =  | accessdate = 29 April 2010 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170628114242/http://www.marci-kids.com/eerintro.html | archive-date = 2017-06-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>沉默回流，<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Koufman JA |title=Laryngopharyngeal reflux is different from classic gastroesophageal reflux disease |journal=Ear, Nose, & Throat Journal |volume=81 |issue=9 Suppl 2 |pages=7–9 |year=2002 |pmid=12353431 |doi= |url=}}</ref>以及「上食道回流」。<ref name="pmid20067549">{{cite journal|vauthors=Zerbib F, Stoll D | title=Management of laryngopharyngeal reflux: an unmet medical need. | journal=Neurogastroenterol Motil | year= 2010 | volume= 22 | issue= 2 | pages= 109–12 | pmid=20067549 | doi=10.1111/j.1365-2982.2009.01437.x }}</ref>

